00:30:21.270 --> 00:30:22.890
Being a parent of
one of those, I'm

00:30:22.890 --> 00:30:24.530
curious to get your
perspective on it.

00:30:24.530 --> 00:30:24.890
LINUS LARSSON: Right.

00:30:24.890 --> 00:30:27.850
So you're talking specifically
about online games and the kind

00:30:27.850 --> 00:30:28.440
of culture that evolves there?

00:30:28.440 --> 00:30:29.856
AUDIENCE: In
particular, he spends

00:30:29.856 --> 00:30:32.740
