that there's no codified way

00:32:26.330 --> 00:32:27.990
to talk about it yet.

00:32:27.990 --> 00:32:32.930
And I was wondering if you guys
have any thoughts about where

00:32:32.930 --> 00:32:36.015
that will come from or what
